workflow:

take spreadsheet listing beers (.xls)
export to csv (beers.csv)
run csv2initcasks to generate a casklist
  e.g. ./csv2initcasks.pl < beers.csv > casklist.csv

run stillage.pl to arrange casks
  e.g. ./stillage.pl casklist.csv
  hit CTRL-A for auto-arrange 
  CTRL-S to save (always auto-arrange first to assign positions)

(run hackfacings to add facing labels)

run layout.py to generate stillage plan and labels

convert labels.ps and stillage.ps to pdf if desired.
